<h1>Monthly Rollups</h1>
<p>Thirty-day rollups synthesised from daily (and, when available, weekly) digests — month at a glance, top 10 stories, and the categorised story list.</p>

{% set list = collections.monthly | reverse %}
{% if list.length === 0 %}
<p><em>No monthly digests yet.</em></p>
{% else %}
<ul class="digest-list">
{% for d in list %}
  <li>
    <time datetime="{{ d.date | isoDate }}">{{ d.date | isoDate }}</time>
    <a href="{{ d.url | absUrl }}">{{ d.data.title }}</a>
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
{% endif %}
